REMARKS: Diagnostic horizons and features recognized in this pedon are:
1. ochric epipedon - the zone from the surface to a depth of 23 centimeters (A, BA horizons);
2. argillic horizon - the zone from 23 to 107 centimeters (Bt1, Bt2, Btx horizons);
3. fragipan - the zone from 56 to 107 centimeters (Btx).
